      "description": "Hey there, neighbor! I\u2019m finally ready to pass the keys of my absolute pride and joy to someone who will love it as much as I have. This beauty has been my 'garage queen'\u2014always pampered, hand-washed, and kept tucked away from the elements. It honestly feels like stepping back in time when you get behind the wheel; the finish is stunning and it drives like a dream. You might find a microscopic mark if you really hunt for it, but to any enthusiast, she\u2019s a total knockout. Come by, grab a coffee, and see for yourself why I\u2019m so proud of this one!",
